INSERT INTO series_references (
                id,
                library_id,
                tmdb_id,
                title,
                theme_color,
                created_at
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
            ON CONFLICT (tmdb_id, library_id) WHERE (tmdb_id IS NOT NULL) DO UPDATE SET
                title = EXCLUDED.title,
                theme_color = EXCLUDED.theme_color,
                updated_at = NOW()
            RETURNING id
